      <title>TSS AAs</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=wizardbalance&amp;message.id=4779#M4779</link>
      <description>&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;B&gt;Potential of Serpentspine&lt;/B&gt; - 5 Ranks - Prereq: Chaotic Potential rank 5&lt;BR&gt;Raises your max stat cap per rank by 5.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;Death's Door&lt;/B&gt; - 5 Ranks - Prereq: Prolonged Mortality rank 5&lt;BR&gt;Increases by 50 HP per rank how far below zero hp you can go without dying.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;Combat Medic&lt;/B&gt; - 5 Ranks - Prereq: Bandage Wounds rank 5&lt;BR&gt;Increases healing via bandages&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;Fast Healing&lt;/B&gt; - 5 Ranks - Prereq: Convalscence at rank2&lt;BR&gt;Raise HP regen by 1 per rank&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;Quick Draw&lt;/B&gt; - 1 Rank&lt;BR&gt;Add 1 slot to potion belt&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;Battle Ready&lt;/B&gt; - 1 Rank&lt;BR&gt;Add 1 slot to bandolier&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;Glyph of Dragon Scales&lt;/B&gt; - 1 Rank - Expendable&lt;BR&gt;Absorb 20% of incoming damage from spells/melee, 10K max - Lasts 1 minute&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;Glyph of Arcane Secrets&lt;/B&gt; - 1 Rank - Expendable&lt;BR&gt;Spell Haste 20% and Mana Preservation 20%&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;Glyph of Draconic Potential&lt;/B&gt; - 1 Rank - Expendable&lt;BR&gt;Increase HP/Mana caps by 750 - Does not fill them up&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;Glyph of Destruction&lt;/B&gt; - 1 Rank - Expendable&lt;BR&gt;Increases damage done by Melee Crits by 10%&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;Labyrinthine Mind&lt;/B&gt; - 5 Ranks - Prereq: Expansive Mind rank 5&lt;BR&gt;Increase item based Mana Regen cap by 1 per rank&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;Mana Fury&lt;/B&gt; - 3 Ranks - Prereq: Mastery of Fury rank 3&lt;BR&gt;Increase damage of critical spells, rank 3 is 20%&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;Sleight of Hand&lt;/B&gt; - 3 Ranks - Prereq: Spell Casting Subtlety rank 3&lt;BR&gt;Increase SCS by 1% per rank&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;Gift or Radiant Mana&lt;/B&gt; - 1 Rank - Prereq: Gift of Mana rank 2&lt;BR&gt;Makes Gift of Mana proc off and usable by spells above level 70&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;Volatile Mana Blaze&lt;/B&gt; - 3 Ranks - Prereq: Mana Blaze rank 1&lt;BR&gt;Increase manaburn&lt;BR&gt;Rank 1: 10000 mana 40000 damage&lt;BR&gt;Rank 2: 11000 mana 44000 damage&lt;BR&gt;Rank 3: 12000 mana 48000 damage&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;Twisted Root&lt;/B&gt; - 3 Ranks - Prereq: Hastened Root rank 3&lt;BR&gt;Lowers recast time on Strong root by 10 minutes per level and makes it less likely to break in combat&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;Arcane Whisper&lt;/B&gt; - 3 Ranks - Prereq: Spell Casting Subtlety rank 3&lt;BR&gt;Decrease Hate by 500/tick for 10 ticks&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;Dimensional Instability&lt;/B&gt; - 1 Rank&lt;BR&gt;Using this will cause you to shadowstep and gain 50% melee mitigation, max 10k and lower your hate generation by 60% while its active. Should take place over 3 ticks.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;Cryomancy&lt;/B&gt; - 3 Ranks&lt;BR&gt;Casting cold spells above level 60 has the following effect:&lt;BR&gt;Rank 1: 5% Chance to cast Snare and lower cold resist by 50 on mob&lt;BR&gt;Rank 2: 10% Chance to cast Snare and lower cold resist by 50 on mob&lt;BR&gt;Rank 3: 15% Chance to cast Snare and lower cold resist by 50 on mob&lt;BR&gt;Effect is unresistable and lasts 5 ticks&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;Volatile Mana&lt;/B&gt; - 3 Ranks - Prereq: Advanced Fury of Magic Mastery rank 2&lt;BR&gt;Increase crit rate by 1% per rank&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;Loyal Familiar&lt;/B&gt;- 1 Rank - Prereq: Devoted Familiar&lt;BR&gt;Resists: +40&lt;BR&gt;Effective Casting Level +9&lt;BR&gt;See Invis level 1&lt;BR&gt;Increase Mana Pool 750&lt;BR&gt;Increase Mana Regen 12/tick&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;Ro's Incendiary Familiar&lt;/B&gt; - 1 Rank - Prereq: Ro's Greater Familar&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;Eci's Icesheen Familiar&lt;/B&gt; - 1 Rank - Prereq: Eci's Greater Familar&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;Druzzil's Arcane Familiar&lt;/B&gt; - 1 Rank - Prereq: Druzzil's Greater Familar&lt;BR&gt;Increase Spell Damage 30% in resist type of familiar&lt;BR&gt;See Invis level 1&lt;BR&gt;Increase resist 60 in resist type of familiar&lt;BR&gt;Increase Mana Pool 500&lt;BR&gt;Increase Mana Regen 4/tick&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;Arcane Overkill&lt;/B&gt; - 3 Ranks&lt;BR&gt;10% cumulative chance per rank of granting your 500 mana when you get the killshot on a nontrivial mob.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&lt;B&gt;Mental Serenity&lt;/B&gt; - 5 Ranks - Prereq: Mental Clarity rank 3&lt;BR&gt;Increase natural Mana Regen 1 per rank&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;!--  / message  --&gt;&lt;!--  edit note  --&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;</description>
