      <title>The Real Top 10 Wizard Class issue:</title>
      <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=wizardbalance&amp;message.id=4713#M4713</link>
      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;font size="3"&gt;&lt;font face="Century"&gt;Since nobody has updated our class issue's thread in almost 7 months now, I thought I'd sit down and write out what I think are our biggest class issues are.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;1.&amp;nbsp; Damage - My main is a wizzy, I've played up through Anguish have my 2.0 ect.&amp;nbsp; I'm oom after every fight, rarely get resists.. and i'm still 50-100k below my guilds best mage in damage delt.&amp;nbsp; For example, on an easy fight like Matriarch Shyra i'll typically do 150-160k damage over the course of the fight.&amp;nbsp; Meanwhile, mages are doing closer to 200k damage, and a good rogue can do almost double my damage over the course of that short fight.&amp;nbsp; Something's wrong here and it needs to be addressed.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;2. Agro Management - This sorta relates to the issue above..&amp;nbsp; When a tank drops suddenly, its only natural for the dps classes to grab agro and get summoned.&amp;nbsp; However, 9 out of 10 times the wizards / mages get summoned while the necros fd, and by the time the melee dps (often doing more damage ironically) is on Hott, another tank is able to pick the mob up.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;3. Mana Regen - 33 with maxed aa's and the devoted familiar hardly cuts it.&amp;nbsp; In a raid situation where I have a bard present, and maybe a necro with MW, its fine, however in a group situation with just c6 and my aa's, after about 10 min I have to med, or whip out my voodoo wand and put my 2.0 away.&amp;nbsp; The bigger picture to this though is that with an 11k+ mana pool its very hard to regain mana with a mere 33 mana regen.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;4. Frenzied / Prolonged Destruction - Who in there right mind would use this?? Double the mana cost for an increased chance to maybe crit.&amp;nbsp; So now instead of being able to nuke hard for 5 min straight, I can nuke for maybe 1 min with my best nuke and be out of mana?&amp;nbsp; And at the cost of 33 aa's?&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;5. Transportation - Way back when we were the masters of transportation.. now we are the cab ride at the end of a night for most raids and thats about it.&amp;nbsp; Some sort of Teleporation type spell or spells needs to go in that would allow us to send entire raids to popular zones.. IE Teleport WoS, Nek Forest, Arcstone, Ect.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;6. Mana Burn - Still pretty much a toy for killing named mobs solo, beyond that I can't say i'd ever use this.. you tried, you failed, at this point, take it out and fix one of the above issues.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Mind you these are just the things that I feel are our biggest issues.&amp;nbsp; If your a younger wizard or haven't progressed far enough yet to have you 1.5/2.0 things like agro are going to be a much bigger issue.&amp;nbsp; At any rate feel free to critque, debate, whatever.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
